column2: SELECT p.objId, p.ra, p.dec, p.petror9#_r, p.expAB_r, p.dered_u as u, p.dered_g as g, p.dered_r as r, p.dered_i as i, s.z, s.plate, s.mjd, s.fiberid, p.petroMag_g as petrog, p.petroMag_r as petror, p.petroMag_i as petroi, pz.absMagU as amu, pz.absMagG as amg, pz.absMagR as amr, pz.absMagI as ami, n.sersic_n as sersic_n, pz.dered_u as ured, pz.dered_g as gred, pz.dered_r as rred, pz.dered_i as ired, FROM galaxy AS p JOIN SpecObj AS s ON s.bestobjid = p.objid JOIN Photoz as pz ON pz.objID = p.objID JOIN nsatlas AS n ON n.mjd = s.mjd and n.fiberID = s.fiberID and n.plate = s.plate WHERE p.petror9#_r > # and p.ra between # and # and s.z < # and p.g < #
